            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "The hard limit is [in Cython](https://github.com/cython/cython/blob/05111636cff6ca9e1777480ff894e85afd63fdd3/Cython/Compiler/Options.py#L144).\r\n\r\nSearch for `ndim` in `Cython/Compiler/`, that should point you to most of the interesting compile time decisions.",
